\newlabel{fig_3}{{3}{7}{Average fractal dimension $D_f$ as a function of the diffusion parameter $T_s$ on a log-linear plot. Error bars are shown in red. The fractal dimension increases from $D_f = 1.708 \pm 0.005$ at $T_s = 2$ to $D_f = 1.963 \pm 0.001$ for $T_s = 8192$}{figure.3}{}}
